high_descs: Turn left, then turn right, then turn right to go to the counter with the red vase.
Pick up the spoon to the left of the salt.
Turn left to face the counter next to the stove.
Place the spoon in the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon on the counter.
Look up to the cabinets above the counter.
Place the bowl in the rightmost cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it in a cabinet.

high_descs: walk to the other corner of the room and face the kitchen counter to the right of the stove
grab the spoon off the top part of the kitchen counter
turn left and face the kitchen counter immediately right of the stove
place the spoon inside the bowl on the counter
pick up the bowl off of the counter with the spoon in it
look up at the cupboards above the counter
place the bowl inside of the cupboards above the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: place a bowl with a spoon in the cupboards in the kitchen

high_descs: Take a step forwards and then turn left and head into the kitchen turning to the right after the counter walk towards the corner then finally turn right towards the counter with the red vase.
Pick up the large spoon on the higher part of the counter behind the red vase.
Turn to the left and note the glass bowl on the counter.
Place the spoon in the glass bowl.
Pick up the glass bowl with the spoon still in it.
Look upwards at the cupboard above the counter.
Open the right door of the cupboard and put the glass bowl with the spoon into the cupboard closing the door afterwards.
anns.task_desc: Put the glass bowl with spoon in the cupboard.
